<script>

document.onreadystatechange = function(e)
{
    if (document.readyState === 'complete')
    {
        var filterPid = null;
        var filterFreguesia = null;
        var filterPredio = null;
        
        if(!window.location.toString().includes("d-7672090-fn_pid=&")){
            filterPid = document.getElementById("d-7672090-fn_pid");
            var pidValue = filterPid.value;
        } else {
            var pidValue = "%25";
        }
        
        if(!window.location.toString().includes("d-7672090-fn_imoveis_colossus.freguesia=&")){
            filterFreguesia = document.getElementById("d-7672090-fn_imoveis_colossus_freguesia");
            var pidFreguesia = filterFreguesia.value;
            pidFreguesia = pidFreguesia.replace("'", "%25");
        }else {
            var pidFreguesia = "%25";
        }
        
        if(!window.location.toString().includes("d-7672090-fn_imoveis_colossus.predio=&")){
            filterPredio = document.getElementById("d-7672090-fn_imoveis_colossus_predio");
            var pidPredio = filterPredio.value;
        } else {
            var pidPredio = "%25";
        }
        
        if(window.location.toString().includes("d-7672090-fn_imoveis_colossus.predio=&") || window.location.toString().includes("d-7672090-fn_imoveis_colossus.freguesia=&") || window.location.toString().includes("d-7672090-fn_pid=&")){
            window.location = "#request.scheme#://#request.serverName#:#request.serverPort##request.contextPath#/web/userview/colossus/listaProcessos/_/listaProcessos?d-7672090-fn_imoveis_colossus.predio="+ pidPredio +"&d-7672090-fn_imoveis_colossus.freguesia="+ pidFreguesia +"&d-7672090-p=1&d-7672090-ps=10&d-7672090-fn_pid=" + pidValue + "&OWASP_CSRFTOKEN=SJ3A-1MYG-D4C4-TJZL-E8HZ-F7EH-O23P-E5EY";
            //window.location = "http://192.168.0.104:8080/jw/web/userview/colossus/listaProcessos/_/listaProcessos?d-7672090-fn_imoveis_colossus.predio=%25&d-7672090-p=1&d-7672090-ps=10&d-7672090-fn_pid=" + filterPid.value + "&OWASP_CSRFTOKEN=SJ3A-1MYG-D4C4-TJZL-E8HZ-F7EH-O23P-E5EY";
        }
        
        
        
        
    }
};


    $(document).ready(function(){
        $("#filters_listaProcessos input[type = submit]").val("Filtrar");
        var input_predio = $("#d-7672090-fn_imoveis_colossus_predio");
        var input = $("#d-7672090-fn_imoveis_colossus_freguesia");
        var input_pid = $("#d-7672090-fn_pid");
        
        $('div.datalist-error').hide();
        
        if(input.val() == '%'){
            input.val("");
        }
        
        if(input.val().includes('%')){
            var novo_valor = input.val().replace("%","'");
            input.val(novo_valor);
        }
        
        if(input_predio.val() == '%'){
            input_predio.val("");
        }
        
        if(input_pid.val() == '%'){
            input_pid.val("");
        }
    });
    
    
    
    
</script>
